Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since when was it?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:36.11,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}are itsukarada?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Being honest became whining{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:39.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}honne ga yowane ni nattana{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Standing firm became strength{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.58,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nigenai koto ga tsuyosa ni natta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have you found it yet?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:44.87,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa mitsukaranai?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not confidence, your true self{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:49.25,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jishin janaku jibun jishin{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There must be something\NI've forgotten that I still haven't found{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:54.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kitto mada sagasetenai wasuremono ga aruhazu{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.93,0:00:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Words I want to say\NThat I still haven't said{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.93,0:00:59.10,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}zutto mada tsutaetenai tsutaetai kotoba{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.26,0:01:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you would watch me, I'd captivate you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.26,0:01:04.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mitete kurerunara misete miserunoni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Truly loving myself{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:09.44,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku ga boku wo aishinuku koto{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it alright to still believe in that?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:13.61,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa mada shinjitemo iika?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I smolder because I've actually burned{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:17.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kusuburuno wa chanto moeta karada{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter where this journey takes us{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:22.74,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doko e mukau tabi datoshitemo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll just open my eyes{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:27.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada me wo mihiraite{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.87,0:01:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And dream my dream{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.87,0:01:31.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yume wo miru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And know my dream{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:33.80,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yume wo shiru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.14,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,TO THE FINAL BATTLEGROUND
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, warriors from around the world\Nwill gather in Carl Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The time to begin\Nour counterattack has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.51,0:02:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But where is everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Did their training not work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How did your training go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll just have to see in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! There's Popp, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Aw, I thought I'd be the first back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you learned\Na pretty intense spell there, Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Sir Matorif with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. About Mentor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, "I'm tired,\Nso I'm going to sleep."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, "I leave the rest to all of you."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that leaves three people.\NDai, Hyunckel, and Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean two people!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That leaves Dai and Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, those two will probably\Ntake the longest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Since they need\Ntheir weapons restored, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you all waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, did you master the ways\Nof the strongest sword?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That doesn't sound reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I did what I could\Nin the time we had.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me this before you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a novice with the spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,With a sword, you could have matched me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,this spear was a parting gift\Nfrom a dying friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A good answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never met anyone able to entrust\Ntheir life to their weapon like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to teach that spirit to Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's with those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Who else is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Book of Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Master Aban's book?\NI've never seen it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... They're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to Master Aban's homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to bring this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. Our master.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one who started all of this.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without Master Aban,\Nme, Popp, and Maam...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and even Hyunckel and Crocodine\Nwouldn't be here like this today!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! Let's go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This battle will be fought by all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I hid my presence and you still sensed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder King Ban\Nregards you with caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Finding you was quite a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think the legendary Dragon Knight\Nwould be hiding in this remote cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't possibly\Nbe looking to take my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What else would an assassin do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Dark King Ban's will?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He made a promise to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans are filth\Nthat pollute the Surface World.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He promised to wipe out the humans\Nand to create a paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked that I cooperate\Nand not oppose him until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I served under Hadorra\Nand fought on the front lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that promise a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.\NEverything King Ban said was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed the humans will be wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But it won't be just the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The monsters and Dragons and Darklings...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Every creature that lives\Non the Surface World will be exterminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, to erase\Nthe Surface World itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,is King Ban's true objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You fought Abyss Dragon King Veruza,\Nso you should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep below the ground\Nwhere we stand right now
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,lies another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Underworld?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Correct. The land of darkness\Nthat the gods gave to the Darklings.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A world of chaos where\Nstrength is the only rule.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:09:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}King Ban's true wish is to raise\Nthe Underworld to the Surface World.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a secret that not even Hadorra,\Nhis most powerful servant, knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it sound wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Surface World erased,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and humans and monsters and Dragons\Nall fall to the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And only the powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and those who enjoy destruction and\Nslaughter can survive in this new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is King Ban's paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am to eliminate\Nany potential threat to that cause!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What you described...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is what people call Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's been fully restored?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:10:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Demon Dragon Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My Reaper Flute neutralizes the senses.\NYet it didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This man is more than a simple beast...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's your intent,\Nthen I have ideas of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,May the great gods of Papunica bless you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, look at how small Papunica is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Off to the field of battle!\NFarewell dear homeland!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or something like that, Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite the poet, Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be pathetic if you run away\Nafter saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on. Do you still think of me\Nas the cowardly chicken?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only way back in the beginning\Nthat I acted like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,For quite a while back in the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad Meruru came\Nsince she can sense enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but why is Miss Amy here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You always stay back to protect Papunica.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm here as Her Majesty's bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know\Nwhat dangers may threaten her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I can lend\Na bit of a hand in a fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.77,0:12:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's all you can do, then you won't\Nsurvive the forces of the Field of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick to guarding the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Amy's acting kind of suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How so? What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole "for the man I love" thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can Popp be so perceptive\Nwhen it comes to other people?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The leaders of the world have gathered\Npowerful warriors there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's worth having Amy there\Neven to just help and heal them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Princess...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. Powerful warriors from all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they're like!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hope they're even\Nhalf as good as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Powerful warriors...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Hyunckel?\NSomething worrying you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand what the Princess is saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important that\Nthe people of the world stand together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to drag too many innocents\Ninto this fight with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never actually seen his face,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've felt the Dark King's\Nimmense presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not someone\Nany normal being can stand up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,True. I know how you feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:49.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}GIGABRAKE{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:54.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,REAPER FLUTE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really the place, Leona?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. This is where Carl Castle used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Army demolished it,\Nleaving nothing behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Our base should be near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Aban's homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But this isn't the time\Nto get sentimental.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It reaches to the top of the clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's their stronghold,\Nit's unbelievably huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the Dark Army is saying,\N"We know you're here. Come and get us."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's prepare!\NWe don't know what'll happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Wait a minute! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Bengana Kingdom\NTank Unit commander, Akhim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw your balloon and came to greet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You? We thought you might be an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up? Did you have to shave your head\Nbecause you lost the tank unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always been bald, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, have you all seen\Nwhat happened to the Field of Death?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We saw from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that will save us time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,General Bowson awaits you\Nat the base of operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you the way. Please follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NAre all the warriors there, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No. The warriors aren't\Nat the base of operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:17:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of them went\Nto the shipbuilding base in Sababa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's Sababa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A small fishing port north of Carl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're secretly building a large ship\Nto take us to the Field of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be almost thirty of us\Nall together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need a large ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, where did Chiu go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You! Where did you come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to infiltrate\Nthe Field of Death,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and gather information\Non the Dark Army for everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I going to cross the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me, my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm currently worthy\Nof the title of Beast King!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Beast King Flute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Crocodine gave it to me\Nas thanks for helping him train!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wonderful item that lures monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can beat them,\Nthey become my followers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, I'll eventually form\Na mighty legion of good monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, let's blow this at the sky\Nand get a flying follower.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:18:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I guess they sometimes come in groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can I beat them?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's almost complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll ride to the Field of Death in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Army?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You peons are annoying us\Nfrom the opposite shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Get real!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a lot of nerve\Ncoming here alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have preferred to come alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fighting all five\Nof the Hadorra Royal Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And now all the world's warriors\Nhave gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.86,0:20:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left is to wait for our ship\Nto be completed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,An attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's someone\Nlanding with a Rura spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the mage Fobster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:21:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's an emergency!\NSababa's been attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A bunch of silver metal beings\Nattacked the dock!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hadorra Royal Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They're strong! They're incredibly strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used Rura to come back and report!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go help them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.74,0:21:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Rura can't go anywhere\Nwe've never been before!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.37,0:21:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we just need to fly north!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If Popp and I go on ahead...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all the help they need.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Nova.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They call me the Hero of the North.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.36,0:22:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you face the devil\NWith logic on your side{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.36,0:22:07.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatoe akuma ni seiron kazashite\Nmukatte mitemo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may just be a rationalization{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:11.28,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sore wa akumade seitouka\Nsashite chigai wa naikamo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.45,0:22:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, even now I waver{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.45,0:22:15.37,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima mo ima mo yureteiru kedo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far will we go?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:19.42,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wa dokomade yukuno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard a voice like an angel's whisper{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:22.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tenshi no sasayaki nimo nita\Nkoe ga kikoeta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was an imposter's illusion\NIt still rang in my ears{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:26.63,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hatamata petenshi no mayakashi\Nhitokiwa mimi ni hibiiteita{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exposed to love and sorrow{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:30.34,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni hiai ni sarasare nagara{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the path strewn with pride{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:34.64,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hokori mamire michi no tochu{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.35,0:22:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fleeting moments of cowardice{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.35,0:22:38.69,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kiete wa ukabu touhikou{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.23,0:22:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The SOS I held back{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.23,0:22:42.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nomikonda SOS{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.07,0:22:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I clenched my trembling fist{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.07,0:22:48.07,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}furueru te wo nigirishimeta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That single little promise{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:53.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatta hitotsu no chiisana yakusoku ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.83,0:22:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those trivial little memories{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.83,0:22:57.45,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}honno sasaina omoidetachi ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:22:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're still in my heart{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:22:59.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}itsumade tattemo kono mune wo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.92,0:23:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As embers that keep me burning{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.92,0:23:03.92,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kogashi tsuzukeru tomoshibi ni naru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A single transparent beam of light{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:08.42,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitosuji no toumei na hikari ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.59,0:23:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lights the way before me{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.59,0:23:11.59,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}me no mae wo terashite yuku{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is little that I can do{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.27,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku ni dekiru koto wa ikutsu mo naisa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.43,0:23:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just keep on to the future\NI managed to grasp through my faith{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.43,0:23:22.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shinjinuita saki ni te ni shita mirai wo\Nsusunde yuke{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.07,0:23:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Dark Army attacked\Nthe port town of Zababa.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.95,0:23:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nova, the Hero of the North goes to help.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.33,0:23:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for him there are\NHadorra's Orichalcum warriors.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.46,0:23:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nova uses his greatest attack\Nto fight against Hym.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.76,0:23:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But no one has yet seen the true terror\Nof the Hadorra Royal Guard.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.14,0:23:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.64,0:23:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Hadorra Royal Guard"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.60,0:23:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i}
